description:
Experience your favorite Marvel Heroes & Villains in epic pinball form in Marvel Pinball Collection 1, an incredible collection that brings together a bunch of exciting Marvel Pinball tables from the masters at Zen Studios!

Marvel Pinball Collection 1 features the following tables:

        • Captain America
        • Doctor Strange
        • Fantastic Four
        • Iron Man
        • Spider-Man
        • Blade
        • Wolverine
        • Ghost Rider
        • Thor
        • X-Men
        • Moon Knight
name: Pinball FX - Marvel Pinball Collection 1
